<template>
    <el-tree :data="data" :props="defaultProps" @node-click="handleNodeClick">
    </el-tree>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            data: [{
                label: '用户管理',
                children: [{
                    label: '学生信息',
                }, {
                    label: '教师信息',
                }]
            }, {
                label: '选题管理',
                children: [{
                    label: '审核课题',
                }, {
                    label: '课题信息',
                }]
            }, {
                label: '系统管理',
                children: [{
                    label: '系统设置',
                }]
            }],
            defaultProps: {
                children: 'children',
                label: 'label'
            }
        };
    },
    methods: {
        handleNodeClick(data) {
            console.log(data);
        }
    }
};
</script>

<style scoped>
.el-tree {
    height: 600px;
}
</style>
